body:
   Greetings,
this PR aims to add several plots to the Payload Inspector for the three types of `CondFormat` objects in which Tracker Alignment conditions are stored:  
   * `TrackerAlignment` : 
     * Difference between two alignment payloads (IOVs) for translations and rotations, plotted by `DetId` index;
     * Difference between two alignment payloads (IOVs) for translations and rotations, aggregated by sub-detector;
     * Trend plot of the position of the translational coordinates for the Pixel Barrel barycenter;

   * `TrackerAlignmentErrorsExtended`:
     * Summary of the APE values by element of the error matrix in each sub-detector, for a single IOV;
     * TrackerMap of the APE values by element of the error matrix, for a single IOV;
     * Detailed average values of the APE by element of the error matrix by Tracker sub-sector (same granularity as used for the derivation), for a single IOV;
      * Detailed comparison between two palyoads (IOVs) of the average APE element of the error matrix, by Tracker sub-sector (same granularity as used for the payload derivation).

   * `TrackerSurfaceDeformations`:
     * Summary of the values for each of (up-to 13) parameters describing the surface deformation broken down by sub-detector;
     * Comparison between two IOVs  of the values for each of (up-to 13) parameters describing the surface deformation broken down by sub-detector;
     * Tracker Map of the Surface deformation parameters, for a single IOV;
     * Tracker Map of the differences between two IOV of the Surface deformation parameters;
     * Detailed average values of the Surface Deformation for each parameter, by Tracker sub-sector (same granularity as used for the APE).

A dedicated unit test is added, as well as few testing scripts.
@ghellwig @hroskes you might want to follow.
